A Markov chain maps current states to possible future states, usually defined with probabilities.
MultiOrderMarkovChain<T> - Class in net.joeclark.proceduralgeneration
A very simple implementation of net.joeclark.proceduralgeneration.MarkovChain that stores the possible outcome states for each given state, but doesn't learn relative probabilities.
